{"type": "article", "id": 20006, "title": "爱心音响", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-31T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145834awdKBVoYHuhskOyr.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tMUAH 是一个新成立的电子品牌，团队以中国设计师为主，他们热衷于做有趣味的音响。这支音响做成了半个爱心的形状，装饰以艳丽的大红色和带流动感的线条，两个凑在一起正好组成完整的爱心。它的底部有磁力连接口，可以吸附在有磁性的地方，或者配对形成左右声道。有白色和红色两种，一对售价 520 元。适合做情人节的礼物，<a href=\"http://izhongchou.taobao.com/dreamdetail.htm?spm=a215p.1472805.0.0.C4FmdD&amp;id=10057824\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150320PLMomxfBAhVqyE9t.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"699\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150321sypJdARGCaThuvID.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"699\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150321gBXoVRaEG2mhnYfv.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"699\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261503228RHO5Zxqtcyk2bnm.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"699\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150323hL5v0bzURXBc4VMP.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"513\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}